{"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"+ (","kind":"text"},{"text":"void","preciseIdentifier":"c:v","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setShowPushnotificationAlert:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL","text":"BOOL"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"show"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"parameters":[{"name":"show","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"YES to show alerts in foreground, NO to suppress them (default)","type":"text"}]}]}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","text":"Discussion","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"By default, iOS does not display notification banners when the app is in the foreground."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"Enable this to show system notification alerts even when the app is active.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Example","text":"Example"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Configure based on app type:"}]},{"syntax":"swift","code":["class NotificationConfigManager {","","    func configureForAppType(_ appType: AppType) {","        switch appType {","        case .messaging:","            \/\/ Messaging apps typically handle notifications in-app","            Pushwoosh.configure.setShowPushnotificationAlert(false)","","        case .ecommerce, .news:","            \/\/ E-commerce and news apps benefit from showing all notifications","            Pushwoosh.configure.setShowPushnotificationAlert(true)","","        case .game:","            \/\/ Games might want to suppress during gameplay","            Pushwoosh.configure.setShowPushnotificationAlert(false)","        }","    }","","    func temporarilyDisableForegroundAlerts(during action: () -> Void) {","        let wasEnabled = Pushwoosh.configure.getShowPushnotificationAlert()","        Pushwoosh.configure.setShowPushnotificationAlert(false)","","        action()","","        Pushwoosh.configure.setShowPushnotificationAlert(wasEnabled)","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":"UNUserNotificationCenterDelegate","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and use "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Pushwoosh.ForegroundPush"},{"text":".","type":"text"}]}],"kind":"content"}],"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"metadata":{"symbolKind":"method","role":"symbol","title":"setShowPushnotificationAlert:","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setShowPushnotificationAlert:","kind":"identifier"}],"externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)setShowPushnotificationAlert:","roleHeading":"Type Method","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"setShowPushnotificationAlert:","kind":"identifier"}]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Sets whether to show alert for push notifications when app is in foreground."}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setShowPushnotificationAlert:"},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setshowpushnotificationalert:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"title":"PushwooshCore","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore","abstract":[{"text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK.","type":"text"}],"role":"collection"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PW